Steps you need to follow ,
Install express for that visit https://expressjs.com/
Create express project , by using express command followed by your application name
Instal multer from npm , command npm install -s multer
place where you want your file request to be handled import multer, see index.js
In this project file while be saved in upload folder with random name, in next project i will show you how to arrange your files and their names
